Smart3 PHP Framework install instructions
---------------------------------------------

The installation of Smart3 is simple. Upload the extracted files to a folder somewere
under the document root of the webserver. Create a MySql 4.1 DataBase. 

The following folders must be writeable by php scripts:

    * /cache
    * /config
    * /data
    * /data/common
    * /data/common/captcha
    * /data/misc
    * /data/navigation
    * /data/user
    * /logs

Point your browser to the admin.php file. You should see a setup formular. Follow the instructions.
 
If it is the first time you use Smart3 and you want to test it you should select utf-8 
as character set and let the tables prefix as it is. After successfull submiting the 
form you are forwarded to the login of Smart3.

For testing you can fill the database with the content of the manual after the successfull 
installation. Execute the following sql file using phpMyAdmin in the created database:

/sql/smart3.sql 
